AT DELAWARE

CAA Commissioner's Honor Roll (2021-22)

2023 SEASON

Appeared in 18 matches, and made 11 starts … scored goal in 4-1 over St. Francis (Aug. 31) … had 17 shots, including six shots on goal … 2023 team captain

2022 SEASON

Started 7 of 18 matches...Had two shots and one assist on the season...Scored two of UD's three goals against Elon...Added an assist versus Towson...Played a season-high 69 minutes versus Stony Brook.

2021 SEASON

Appeared in 14 matches...Scored her first collegiate goal against Elon...Added an assist at UNCW...Had eight shots with three on goal for the season...Played a season-high 48 minutes at Hofstra.

2020-21 SEASON

Did not appear in any matches during the season.

HIGH SCHOOL

Attended Germantown Academy.
